pick up the pencil on the shelf of the desk
turn around and then turn left and walk straight to the bed then turn left and walk to the window and turn right and walk straight to the dresser
put the pencil down inside the bowl on the dresser
pick up the bowl and the pencil on the dresser together

high_descs: Turn right, turn right to face the left side of the desk.
Pick up the pen from the second shelf.

Put the pen in the bowl to the right of the lamp.
Pick up the bowl from the dresser.
Turn around and walk back to the desk.
Put the bowl down on the desk to the right of the mug.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall on the other side of the room.  Turn right at the wall and walk to the desk.
Pick up the pen on the first upper shelf of the desk.
Turn around, take a step and turn left.  Walk to the other side of the room to the dresser.
Put the pen standing straight up on the bowl on the dresser.
Pick up the bowl with the pen standing in it.
Turn around and walk to the other side of the room to the desk.  Turn toward the desk.
Put the bowl with the pen down on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a pen in a bowl sitting on a dresser and move it to a desk.
